dan memutar.

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:29.020
Kemudian ngomong sendiri.

00:16:29.220 --> 00:16:33.220
Sedang apa si Naga Pengkutuk
itu kira-kira?

00:16:33.820 --> 00:16:36.120
Aku juga penasaran.

00:16:36.220 --> 00:16:36.930
Raja!

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:37.720
Yang terbaik.

00:16:37.720 --> 00:16:38.480
Rakyat!

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:39.220
Yang terburuk.

00:16:39.220 --> 00:16:40.060
Nyami-nyami!

