Yang terhebat.

00:16:41.120 --> 00:16:42.820
Duaarrr!

00:16:44.220 --> 00:16:45.060
Bagus!

00:16:45.060 --> 00:16:47.700
Bagus sekali!

00:16:47.700 --> 00:16:50.800
Kau belajar cepat sekali, Faf.

